{"tid":330000,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句,窮遊真係慘過食屎","createTime":"2017-07-20T21:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T13:22:36.000Z","uid":23445,"like":224,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"36ec693580b3a26e42592fd118447cca835c0e84","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:34:27.000Z","msg":"窮遊:乜到搵再平,坐長途巴士,住dorm,shared bathroom<br />\n<br />\n係香港住已經成隻狗咁, 估唔到去旅行都要做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 唔好同鬼佬比,人地屋企大到仆街,得閒住下dorm都冇所謂"},{"pid":"612b35c275d2e4107e778f534200196a9e40bc6a","tid":330000,"uid":2419,"like":48,"dislike":8,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:59:11.000Z","msg":"冇錢咪撚學人去旅行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85406d68d4a00ee8d80aa09a1d25fcd39283b949","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇錢咪撚學人去旅行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前冇錢但想玩多幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家不了,寧願玩少幾日,住酒店好撚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af09f051a84a920f2604a93ede4a353a45aa42af","tid":330000,"uid":72990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:53:41.000Z","msg":"連登仔大數都係窮撚 實負評你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7505fa8704f878d327598204103ae6983e8cfc","tid":330000,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔大數都係窮撚 實負評你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger 窮極都二三皮一個月"},{"pid":"516048e010cf2c6b96d5f1347ac9d21d000d6ec3","tid":330000,"uid":18241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:2