s/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔窮遊會唔會考慮包車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1628988517cbcbf3488ca3f224e4f581a0214bed","tid":330000,"uid":281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T01:48:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61c76f07b7d42a5d543b7d68e31b31c316c06eed","tid":330000,"uid":79442,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T01:58:12.000Z","msg":"有次我條女話窮遊，我xyz佢<br />\n之後佢話包左車<br />\n我: 黑人問號???"},{"pid":"bcf94a21e2df4dc8dd92f31a9663e4171a9e6439","tid":330000,"uid":71502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"而家投資下基金都有20-30k既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n旅行就兩個月一次"},{"pid":"267dfb2d2f619423e5078ae12bfc842c7ee782b8","tid":330000,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家投資下基金都有20-30k既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n旅行就兩個月一次</blockquote><br />\n我而家兩季收息都夠走到轉。"},{"pid":"729cd0512be8d0e075a21c680daa36b7c883ac84","tid":330000,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>趕一日得一班車嘅景點真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁辛苦去到可能玩廿分鐘就夠，但可能要等二個鐘先有車走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本好多靚景都係咁架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自駕咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個個識揸車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去呢啲景點睇野唔代表窮遊 可能真係好想睇<br />\n食都可以食好好 又可以shopping<br />\n唔係樣慳住慳住就得啦"},{"pid":"ac62ea6654a024daa26a809d6b67118623899d7c","tid":330000,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:08:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>趕一日得一班車嘅景點真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁辛苦去到可能玩廿分鐘就夠，但可能要等二個鐘先有車走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本好多靚景都係咁架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔窮遊會唔會考慮包車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鳥取呀 北海道美瑛個啲我都包車架<br />\n但有啲地方真係唔係好適合"},{"pid":"90effbd291477a4fe98d4c77845cd3bdd4e8b0a4","tid":330000,"uid":21222,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"窮遊=窮撚想遊行 慘就一定但你又想遊行就係咁嫁啦"},{"pid":"eb5128da8a37d222d695b3f9410b38b6850b5fb4","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮遊=窮撚想遊行 慘就一定但你又想遊行就係咁嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過一次真係不了,慘過大學住dorm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd671a9dc1b6837f3bc0c7f3224eeccbbb3671a7","tid":330000,"uid":121005,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"點都衰唔過d外國人黎賣藝/賣野話支持佢地嘅旅程"},{"pid":"f0611e6524d099e666ad138f22a3ae08b3a5de46","tid":330000,"uid":22560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"住hostel ok<br />\n底線係一定要自己獨立房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2842b4a8c20e57da69f896ee14f2852196ecae84","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點都衰唔過d外國人黎賣藝/賣野話支持佢地嘅旅程</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起就火滾<br />\n好多外國人係香港旅遊景點賣本地紀念品<br />\n一枝香港旗,30hkd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要話自己失聰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6525e4a64dac813b54317d55d55e4e13aafa121","tid":330000,"uid":55,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4867127ca2a33a742109e43761fc99fcf9f36d28","tid":330000,"uid":49754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>窮遊=窮撚想遊行 慘就一定但你又想遊行就係咁嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過一次真係不了,慘過大學住dorm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係大學住慣dorm所以覺得hostel無乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n不過出嚟做返幾年嘢之後去旅行都係酒店為主"},{"pid":"b34f8e08efd57e5d2a1923e540dc1d6fd5c0ef8c","tid":330000,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:22:50.000Z","msg":"個個底線唔同既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我底線係要舒服，<br />\n其實好多時每晚200樓下都有唔少舒服位置好既酒店住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165843665b25717ff8b6a6c84c5e6f93a64d7670","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個底線唔同既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我底線係要舒服，<br />\n其實好多時每晚200樓下都有唔少舒服位置好既酒店住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n義大利,東歐就有<br />\n法國貴到仆街,比班港女吹到上天,我呸"},{"pid":"da097e56e4dc1010b4962310963ccf68ad310c6d","tid":330000,"uid":71243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差極都唔會住hostel 比人偷野仲大鑊</blockquote><br />\n年頭去摩洛哥住過幾間hostel,手機相機ipad擺晒係床去沖涼都無事wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0719a9c6fb7730df548e8c873da68dbc5f3fd67d","tid":330000,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:33:39.000Z","msg":"窮遊L揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d37410d8e96a55481f1056e85820a8f2b67ff6","tid":330000,"uid":32464,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:40:07.000Z","msg":"人地鐘意點旅行人地既事 咁都管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人出國係鐘意個景 唔著重食住係佢地既選擇<br />\n<br />\n你話窮遊完大大聲話一萬玩足三十日好威威寫攻略又話人地嗰啲唔叫旅行 就話姐"},{"pid":"d0d4966f93269da0fafdfebb7bcd2e106f57ab53","tid":330000,"uid":32464,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>差極都唔會住hostel 比人偷野仲大鑊</blockquote><br />\n年頭去摩洛哥住過幾間hostel,手機相機ipad擺晒係床去沖涼都無事wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日睇呢啲都覺得好好笑<br />\n無事係好彩<br />\n唔好覺得日日放係度自己走左去一定無事 <br />\n<br />\n唔係話hostel危險 自己都住過<br />\n但想講 邊度都係 唔應該周圍放貴重物品<br />\n有番啲警覺性會好啲囉"},{"pid":"ec5f45efbe6dde17f6f4323783e242fb95d3cb2b","tid":330000,"uid":78252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>差極都唔會住hostel 比人偷野仲大鑊</blockquote><br />\n年頭去摩洛哥住過幾間hostel,手機相機ipad擺晒係床去沖涼都無事wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日睇呢啲都覺得好好笑<br />\n無事係好彩<br />\n唔好覺得日日放係度自己走左去一定無事 <br />\n<br />\n唔係話hostel危險 自己都住過<br />\n但想講 邊度都係 唔應該周圍放貴重物品<br />\n有番啲警覺性會好啲囉</blockquote><br />\n佢真係誇張左d，日本香港都唔敢咁做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f1041ad9206582224b40e0