generator 世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 井底之蛙</blockquote><br />\n依家好多都玩豪華式hostel (法國summer ～$500hkd 一個床位,一晚,6-8人share)<br />\n<br />\n同樣價錢,大把選擇<br />\n為左識人而住hostel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落pub,酒bar 大把野玩"},{"pid":"4544fef19537332d9ba72b026b26d9459f39f3d0","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將所有洗費用哂係睇show度點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如個成班fd,搵Airbnb, entire home <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHostel 太平真係有d伏+d環境唔太衛生,一係就山卡啦咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7af6432407010306f8cd675ac88aebbaca43c5","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地鐘意點旅行人地既事 咁都管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人出國係鐘意個景 唔著重食住係佢地既選擇<br />\n<br />\n你話窮遊完大大聲話一萬玩足三十日好威威寫攻略又話人地嗰啲唔叫旅行 就話姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身邊好多人以窮遊為榮,串鳩個班豪遊既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搶到平機票都係度打晒飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話人地玩得唔抵/唔識旅遊等等"},{"pid":"7ba19885223e5935cbe006febe9c2b76588e7190","tid":330000,"uid":42426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個個底線唔同既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我底線係要舒服，<br />\n其實好多時每晚200樓下都有唔少舒服位置好既酒店住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n義大利,東歐就有<br />\n法國貴到仆街,比班港女吹到上天,我呸</blockquote><br />\n點睇瑞士?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n瑞士,識玩可以好抵玩<br />\n會覺得物有所值<br />\n情侶去一流,自己一個去會覺得好寂寞</blockquote><br />\n有無好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf3fd1ab1b522ba399a4bf72458e2ac0318f7d1","tid":330000,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T13:26:53.000Z","msg":"上次我去東京5日洗費4000港幣(唔包機票 機票1200)<br />\n如果唔買手信應該3000夠哂<br />\n旅行反而無乜心情想shopping同食野 <br />\n(我反而好撚鐘意食便利店D便當)<br />\n因為好多野香港都有 無乜意義<br />\n一日行3-5個地方<br />\n由朝早10點non-stop咁行到夜晚8點<br />\n住宿搵左包早餐既hostel<br />\n其實計計埋埋我交通先洗得最多 好後悔無帶單車去<br />\n咁我算唔算窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e03575c649e006cf92354737e91e9447615926e","tid":330000,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"一個人住一間房我會好撚驚<br />\n反而得一個床位個D我會有安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋lobby可以同人傾計"},{"pid":"20d4c91fd593f713c1a1bc461921d016eb86df14","tid":330000,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T13:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次我去東京5日洗費4000港幣(唔包機票 機票1200)<br />\n如果唔買手信應該3000夠哂<br />\n旅行反而無乜心情想shopping同食野 <br />\n(我反而好撚鐘意食便利店D便當)<br />\n因為好多野香港都有 無乜意義<br />\n一日行3-5個地方<br />\n由朝早10點non-stop咁行到夜晚8點<br />\n住宿搵左包早餐既hostel<br />\n其實計計埋埋我交通先洗得最多 好後悔無帶單車去<br />\n咁我算唔算窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食野，住宿，交通呢啲無謂野真係冇必要大洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de19271c9f8b0febcf34b1bc5f534b68ecbabea","tid":330000,"uid":13250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"返工已經辛苦,去旅行都難為自己做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54095443ed891e50b9bea5e6dbfa4e58dcba51b7","tid":330000,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"學生既話無辦法，<br />\n豐檢由人，<br />\n後生想去多d地方又無錢去多幾轉咪窮遊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過去得就唔會呻，鬼叫你窮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：趁暑假半窮遊歐洲中，一大部分budget 放左係出街食餐廳 丶景點同d museums既入場券同交通度，<br />\n住對我黎講無咩所謂，<br />\n雖然攰但行程好充實，無後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之不過都希望第時有錢會以&quot;渡假&quot;而唔係&quot;explore&quot;為目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee84431c4077a280ea90ccae762273da5095b80","tid":330000,"uid":51200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"講多少少，去歐洲一定要趁後生去，（尤其中歐東歐巴爾幹） ，<br />\n仲有南美之類，<br />\n唔係你老既時候真係有心無力<br />\n爬kotor座依山而建既城牆<br />\n仲有delos座石山，<br />\n斷斷續續係歐洲行左起碼十幾二十幾座山，上最高既景點<br />\n先體會到後生既可貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後生無錢窮遊下，去多d地方無所謂<br />\n但如果來來去去都係窮遊日本韓國，<br />\n咁你窮遊既意義又係咩？單純打發時間？<br />\n住過Hostel既都知道，好多廿幾歲既鬼佬鬼妹都會窮遊，<br />\n目的係雖然無咩大錢，<br />\n但都想趁後生探索世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題係，有時香港班後生有時寧願一年去幾次日本台灣韓國，<br />\n之後就話無錢去其他地方旅行，<br />\n呢種心態同有無錢，窮遊與否無關<br />\n而係香港人並無一股冒險同作為一位渺小人類探索世界既精神<br />\n過於安於舒適既世界。<br />\n所以，我個人唔認為應該批判窮遊，<br />\n而係應該討論返香港人（由其係後生仔)究竟對「旅行」呢樣野，抱有咩態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ca18131e54ddf28d50834013ad6ab4f41c3b63","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個人住一間房我會好撚驚<br />\n反而得一個床位個D我會有安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋lobby可以同人傾計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好彩姐,仲未預到不愉快經歷"},{"pid":"787d352e4f22afa61bbf7d90f63f202636f8133f","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個人住一間房我會好撚驚<br />\n反而得一個床位個D我會有安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋lobby可以同人傾計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好彩姐,仲未遇到不愉快經歷</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9f76f25090b4d711ef91e76a73021a2d504e222e","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講多少少，去歐洲一定要趁後生去，（尤其中歐東歐巴爾幹） ，<br />\n仲有南美之類，<br />\n唔係你老既時候真係有心無力<br />\n爬kotor座依山而建既城牆<br />\n仲有delos座石山，<br />\n斷斷續續係歐洲行左起碼十幾二十幾座山，上最高既景點<br />\n先體會到後生既可貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後生無錢窮遊下，去多d地方無所謂<br />\n但如果來來去去都係窮遊日本韓國，<br />\n咁你窮遊既意義又係咩？單純打發時間？<br />\n住過Hostel既都知道，好多廿幾歲既鬼佬鬼妹都會窮遊，<br />\n目的係雖然無咩大錢，<br />\n但都想趁後生探索世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題係，有時香港班後生有時寧願一年去幾次日本台灣韓國，<br />\n之後就話無錢去其他地方旅行，<br />\n呢種心態同有無錢，窮遊與否無關<br />\n而係香港人並無一股冒險同作為一位渺小人類探索世界既精神<br />\n過於安於舒適既世界。<br />\n所以，我個人唔認為應該批判窮遊，<br />\n而係應該討論返香港人（由其係後生仔)究竟對「旅行」呢樣野，抱有咩態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人並無一股冒險同作為一位渺小人類探索世界既精神<br />\n過於安於舒適既世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67535bcdc3c7d155f997df46b2d27915016b925c","tid":330000,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次我去東京5日洗費4000港幣(唔包機票 機票1200)<br />\n如果唔買手信應該3000夠哂<br />\n旅行反而無乜心情想shopping同食野 <br />\n(我反而好撚鐘意食便利店D便當)<br />\n因為好多野香港都有 無乜意義<br />\n一日行3-5個地方<br />\n由朝早10點non-stop咁行到夜晚8點<br />\n住宿搵左包早餐既hostel<br />\n其實計計埋埋我交通先洗得最多 好後悔無帶單車去<br />\n咁我算唔算窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n800蚊一日淨食+住都okay"},{"pid":"2d069ee4d13e321dd4f135c364a54501e91e3049","tid":330000,"uid":36990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講多少少，去歐洲一定要趁後生去，（尤其中歐東歐巴爾幹） ，<br />\n仲有南美之類，<br />\n唔係你老既時候真係有心無力<br />\n爬kotor座依山而建既城牆<br />\n仲有delos座石山，<br />\n斷斷續續係歐洲行左起碼十幾二十幾座山，上最高既景點<br />\n先體會到後生既可貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後生無錢窮遊下，去多d地方無所謂<br />\n但如果來來去去都係窮遊日本韓國，<br />\n咁你窮遊既意義又係咩？單純打發時間？<br />\n住過Hostel既都知道，好多廿幾歲既鬼佬鬼妹都會窮遊，<br />\n目的係雖然無咩大錢，<br />\n但都想趁後生探索世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題係，有時香港班後生有時寧願一年去幾次日本台灣韓國，<br />\n之後就話無錢去其他地方旅行，<br />\n呢種心態同有無錢，窮遊與否無關<br />\n而係香港人並無一股冒險同作為一位渺小人類探索世界既精神<br />\n過於安於舒適既世界。<br />\n所以，我個人唔認為應該批判窮遊，<br />\n而係應該討論返香港人（由其係後生仔)究竟對「旅行」呢樣野，抱有咩態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人並無一股冒險同作為一位渺小人類探索世界既精神<br />\n過於安於舒適既世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吓我去旅行就係為吃喝玩樂打發時間，唔撚得？"},{"pid":"139d059515d138b5070d13bce49728ee86106091","tid":330000,"uid":39021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地鐘意點旅行人地既事 咁都管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人出國係鐘意個景 唔著重食住係佢地既選擇<br />\n<br />\n你話窮遊完大大聲話一萬玩足三十日好威威寫攻略又話人地嗰啲唔叫旅行 就話姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身邊好多人以窮遊為榮,串鳩個班豪遊既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搶到平機票都係度打晒飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話人地玩得唔抵/唔識旅遊等等</blockquote><br />\n根本窮遊又會串豪遊, 豪遊又會串窮遊, 呢個係香港人中意笑非我種類嘅人嘅問題, 好多時都同窮遊豪遊嘅根本無關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d770074d29fd70934eefb494bd701d6f595bf4","tid":330000,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講多少少，去歐洲一定要趁後生去，（尤其中歐東歐巴爾幹） ，<br />\n仲有南美之類，<br />\n唔係你老既時候真係有心無力<br />\n爬kotor座依山而建既城牆<br />\n仲有delos座石山，<br />\n斷斷續續係歐洲行左起碼十幾二十幾座山，上最高既景點<br />\n先體會到後生既可貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後生無錢窮遊下，去多d地方無所謂<br />\n但如果來來去去都係窮遊日本韓國，<br />\n咁你窮遊既意義又係咩？單純打發時間？<br />\n住過Hostel既都知道，好多廿幾歲既鬼佬鬼妹都會窮遊，<br />\n目的係雖然無咩大錢，<br />\n但都想趁後生探索世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題係，有時香港班後生有時寧願一年去幾次日本台灣韓國，<br />\n之後就話無錢去其他地方旅行，<br />\n呢種心態同有無錢，窮遊與否無關<br />\n而係香港人並無一股冒險同作為一位渺小人類探索世界既精神<br />\n過於安於舒適既世界。<br />\n所以，我個人唔認為應該批判窮遊，<br />\n而係應該討論返香港人（由其係後生仔)究竟對「旅行」呢樣野，抱有咩態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人並無一股冒險同作為一位渺小人類探索世界既精神<br />\n過於安於舒適既世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">吓我去旅行就係為吃喝玩樂打發時間，唔撚得？</span></blockquote><br />\n呢堆野唔係同d充大頭鬼，一年去幾次台灣人韓國既窮撚學生講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係同班真係搵到食既人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你係學生<br />\n你又真係搵到食，你洗撚一年去幾次窮遊日本之後返黎香港咬青瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一年一次半次就話姐<br />\n一年relax幾次咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e00a67a8637bdac1be4784fe2016b800230fe2a","tid":330000,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"冇錢去咩旅行呀，用去旅行既錢係香港玩，狂食好野仲爽啦⋯⋯"},{"pid":"770fe0a1a985d92025c371a58e96977ff8535120","tid":330000,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:41:17.000Z","msg":".."},{"pid":"54af471a615b16dacd652ca9db830d7d0e67047e","tid":330000,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係冇錢，只係覺得唔值得花喺住同交通，寧願買紀念品同食嘢</blockquote><br />\n長途機商務真好唔同...<br />\nDepends 乜國家，大城市一定蠔油<br />\nNYC TOKYO BKK之類"},{"pid":"b88fe5cb3f23931d35747398dbec2ca2a6ad774a","tid":330000,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上次我去東京5日洗費4000港幣(唔包機票 機票1200)<br />\n如果唔買手信應該3000夠哂<br />\n旅行反而無乜心情想shopping同食野 <br />\n(我反而好撚鐘意食便利店D便當)<br />\n因為好多野香港都有 無乜意義<br />\n一日行3-5個地方<br />\n由朝早10點non-stop咁行到夜晚8點<br />\n住宿搵左包早餐既hostel<br />\n其實計計埋埋我交通先洗得最多 好後悔無帶單車去<br />\n咁我算唔算窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食野，住宿，交通呢啲無謂野真係冇必要大洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去東京食野唔大洗，咁為乜?"},{"pid":"7ff7de6bba8948b62b7259d2c507812f51e28d9c","tid":330000,"uid":51200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講多少少，去歐洲一定要趁後生去，（尤其中歐東歐巴爾幹） ，<br />\n仲有南美之類，<br />\n唔係你老既時候真係有心無力<br />\n爬kotor座依山而建既城牆<br />\n仲有delos座石山，<br />\n斷斷續續係歐洲行左起碼十幾二十幾座山，上最高既景點<br />\n先體會到後生既可貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後生無錢窮遊下，去多d地方無所謂<br />\n但如果來來去去都係窮遊日本韓國，<br />\n咁你窮遊既意義又係咩？單純打發時間？<br />\n住過Hostel既都知道，好多廿幾歲既鬼佬鬼妹都會窮遊，<br />\n目的係雖然無咩大錢，<br />\n但都想趁後生探索世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題係，有時香港班後生有時寧願一年去幾次日本台灣韓國，<br />\n之後就話無錢去其他地方旅行，<br />\n呢種心態同有無錢，窮遊與否無關<br />\n而係香港人並無一股冒險同作為一位渺小人類探索世界既精神<br />\n過於安於舒適既世界。<br />\n所以，我個人唔認為應該批判窮遊，<br />\n而係應該討論返香港人（由其係後生仔)究竟對「旅行」呢樣野，抱有咩態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人並無一股冒險同作為一位渺小人類探索世界既精神<br />\n過於安於舒適既世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔岩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整體黎講，你認為香港後生仔既世界觀係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肯踏出第一步出去explore 同淨係識留係 Comfort zone既比例有幾多大家心照啦，<br />\n根本就係青年人對自己，同家長對子女，<br />\n有種過度保護既心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0a485ae8cce30210fd9ed5e6f6472540017af6","tid":330000,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇錢去咩旅行呀，用去旅行既錢係香港玩，狂食好野仲爽啦⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\nOn撚9，駁都廢撚事，<br />\n趁後生出去望多兩眼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95ae882fe4d306c43387de0a34cfadf23a336d9","tid":330000,"uid":78252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係冇錢，只係覺得唔值得花喺住同交通，寧願買紀念品同食嘢</blockquote><br />\n短途交通都okay (8小時以下)<br />\n長途巴士真係不了<br />\n時間又閪,又訓唔到,wifi廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,如果有巴打坐長途巴士既,唔好坐廁所坐近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有人柯屎就仆得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剩係接受到5粒鐘左存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n渣架<img src=\"/as